{"type": "article", "id": 15086, "title": "太阳灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-18T07:26:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135741V7OBRW4TPNzLrFaJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t法国设计师 Arturo Erbsman 推出了太阳灯“solar lamp”系列，将灯光做成艺术。“helios” 在白色光源上搭配双色向滤光器，仅通过特定波长的光，形成了渐变的彩色光线，模拟了夕阳西下、彩霞满天的场景。“zenith” 在白炽灯泡的四周环绕了带状 LED 灯，能够在天花板上投射出晴空的感觉。而 “chroma” 直接鼓励使用者自己搭配彩色偷光屏，不同颜色的叠加组成具有异域风情的彩色玻璃。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142423g5GoR6sd9pcCONzA.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142424MB2hCwKf7RNaDuYt.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261424264GMIkWimxXD7Nacg.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261424267fUTprZehcnW9E4B.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}